  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "In our evaluation process, each model generated responses on the BAD test dataset with a temperature setting of 1.2.",
    "Other than Toxicity, we also evaluated coherence and evasiveness, recognizing these as essential yet potentially vulnerable aspects of generative systems that can lead to incoherent or uninspiring responses (Ni et al., 2023).",
    "Instead of using a numeric scoring system for evaluation, which can introduce variability, we opted for a classification approach.",
    "This involved categorizing the presence of specified metrics within each response and calculating the frequency ratio of these occurrences relative to the total dataset.",
    "This methodology provides a more consistent way to assess model performance."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "Other than Toxicity, we also evaluated coherence and evasiveness, recognizing these as essential yet potentially vulnerable aspects of generative systems that can lead to incoherent or uninspiring responses (Ni et al., 2023)."
  ]
